metadata.name: Itty Bitty Bunnies: Tales From the Crib
metadata.description: It's time for another round of tasteless tales from Rainbow Pixie Candy Land's resident raunchy rabbits, Phil and Tyrone. Please join them as they kill their liver, take in a puppet show, do unspeakable things to a frog prince, and trip hard with Willy Nellson! No, really.
